23 Feb, 2006: [v0.1.1]
	Added install-all rule to Makefile.  Include stdio.h and stdlib.h to
	eliminate warnings about printf and exit, respectively.  those show
	up with gcc 4.0.  Run ranlib after lib has been copied (required for
	ld on Darwin).
